Merriweather Sans Light Regular (MerriweatherSans-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-Light', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. Merriweather Sans Light Regular (MerriweatherSans-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Merriweather Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Merriweather Sans Light'.

Pass

Merriweather Sans Light Italic (MerriweatherSans-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Merriweather Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Merriweather Sans Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Merriweather Sans Regular (MerriweatherSans-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-Regular', Everything looks good.

Merriweather Sans Italic (MerriweatherSans-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-Italic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Merriweather Sans Bold (MerriweatherSans-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-Bold', Everything looks good.

Merriweather Sans ExtraBold Regular (MerriweatherSans-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

Merriweather Sans ExtraBold Regular (MerriweatherSans-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Merriweather Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Merriweather Sans ExtraBold'.

Merriweather Sans ExtraBold Italic (MerriweatherSans-ExtraBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'MerriweatherSans-ExtraBoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Merriweather Sans ExtraBold Italic (MerriweatherSans-ExtraBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Merriweather Sans' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold Italic' = NID 1 'Merriweather Sans ExtraBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.
